{"id":11927,"date":"2024-03-20T18:51:43","date_gmt":"2024-03-20T13:21:43","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/?p=11927"},"modified":"2024-03-30T11:37:34","modified_gmt":"2024-03-30T06:07:34","slug":"add-staff","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/add-staff\/","title":{"rendered":"Add Staff"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe title=\"How to manage Staff Option\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/Tj9M4KS7owM?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"330\" src=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0012-1024x330.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-12048\" style=\"width:661px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0012-1024x330.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0012-500x161.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0012-768x247.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0012.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#cd3636\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Add Staff<\/mark><\/strong> \u0915\u0947 \u092e\u0926\u0926 \u0938\u0947 \u0906\u092a \u0905\u092a\u0928\u0947 \u0938\u092d\u0940 \u0915\u093e\u092e \u0915\u0930\u0928\u0947 \u0935\u093e\u0932\u0947 \u0932\u094b\u0917\u094b\u0902 \u0915\u094b manage \u0915\u0930 \u0938\u0915\u0924\u0947 \u0939\u0948\u0964 \u092f\u0939\u093e \u0905\u092a\u0928\u0947 Staff \u0915\u093e <strong><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\">ID Create<\/mark><\/strong> \u0915\u0930 \u0915\u0947 \u0926\u0947 \u0938\u0915\u0924\u0947 \u0939\u0948\u0964 Staff Add \u0915\u0947 \u092e\u0926\u0926 \u0938\u0947 \u0906\u092a \u0905\u092a\u0928\u0947 Staff \u0915\u094b \u0905\u0932\u0917-\u0905\u0932\u0917 \u0915\u093e\u092e\u094b\u0902 \u0915\u0947 \u0932\u093f\u090f Manage \u0915\u0932\u0930 \u0938\u0915\u0924\u0947 \u0939\u0948\u0964<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0906\u092a\u0915\u094b <mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#cd3636\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Staff ID<\/mark> \u0915\u0948\u0938\u0947 \u092c\u0928\u093e\u0928\u093e \u0939\u0948\u0964 \u0928\u0940\u091a\u0947 \u0938\u092e\u091d\u093e\u092f\u093e \u0917\u092f\u093e \u0939\u0948\u0964  <\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"177\" src=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0011-1024x177.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-12051 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0011-1024x177.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0011-500x87.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0011-768x133.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0011.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<p>\u0907\u0938 Section \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u0906\u092a \u0905\u092a\u0928\u0947 Staff \u0915\u093e <mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\">mobile number <\/mark>\u0921\u093e\u0932\u0947\u0902\u0917\u0947<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"176\" src=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0010-1024x176.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-12050 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0010-1024x176.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0010-500x86.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0010-768x132.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0010.jpg 1061w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<p>\u0908\u0938 Section \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u0906\u092a <mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Password<\/mark> \u092c\u0928\u093e\u090f\u0902\u0917\u0947\u0964 \u091c\u093f\u0938\u0938\u0947 \u0906\u092a\u0915\u094b \u0905\u092a\u0928\u0947 Staff \u0915\u094b \u0926\u0947\u0928\u093e \u0939\u0948\u0964 \u091c\u093f\u0938\u0938\u0947 \u0935\u0939 <mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Log in <\/mark>\u0915\u0930 \u092a\u093e\u090f\u0964 <\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"180\" src=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0009-1024x180.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-12049 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0009-1024x180.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0009-500x88.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0009-768x135.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0009.jpg 1067w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<p>\u092f\u0939\u093e \u092a\u0947 \u0906\u092a \u0905\u092a\u0928\u0947 Staff \u0915\u093e Name \u0921\u093e\u0932\u0947\u0902\u0917\u0947\u0964 <\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"163\" src=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0008-1024x163.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-12052 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0008-1024x163.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0008-500x80.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0008-768x122.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0008.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<p>\u0907\u0938 Section \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u0906\u092a \u0905\u092a\u0928\u0947 Staff \u0915\u093e \u092a\u0942\u0930\u093e <mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Address<\/mark> \u0915\u094b \u0921\u093e\u0932\u0947\u0902\u0917\u0947\u0964 <\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"153\" src=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0007-1024x153.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-12053 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0007-1024x153.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0007-500x75.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0007-768x114.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0007.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<p>\u0907\u0938 Section \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u0906\u092a \u0905\u092a\u0928\u0947 Staff \u0915\u093e <mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Email Id<\/mark> \u0915\u094b \u0921\u093e\u0932\u0947\u0902\u0917\u0947\u0964<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"166\" src=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0002-1024x166.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-12054 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0002-1024x166.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0002-500x81.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0002-768x124.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0002.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<p>Staff Type \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u0906\u092a \u0905\u092a\u0928\u0947 Staff \u0915\u094b \u091a\u0941\u0928 \u0938\u0915\u0924\u0947 \u0915\u093f \u0909\u0928\u0915\u094b \u0915\u093f\u0938 Type \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u0930\u0916\u0928\u093e \u0939\u0948\u0964 1. <mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Staff Type<\/mark> And 2. <mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Delivery Boy<\/mark> Type.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"474\" src=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0005-1024x474.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-12055 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0005-1024x474.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0005-500x231.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0005-768x356.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0005.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<ol>\n<li><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Staff Type<\/mark> \u091c\u094b \u0906\u092a\u0915\u0947 \u0926\u0941\u0915\u093e\u0928 \u0915\u0947 \u0905\u0928\u094d\u0926\u0930 \u0915\u093e\u092e \u0915\u0930\u0902\u0917\u0947\u0964 <br><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Delivery Boy <\/mark>\u091c\u094b \u0906\u092a\u0915\u0947 \u0926\u0941\u0915\u093e\u0928 \u0915\u0947 \u0938\u092e\u093e\u0928 Deliver \u0915\u0930\u0947\u0917\u093e\u0964 <br>\u0907\u0928 \u0926\u094b\u0928\u094b\u0902 \u0915\u094b \u0906\u092a \u0905\u0932\u0917 \u0905\u0932\u0917 \u0930\u0916 \u0938\u0915\u0924\u0947 \u0939\u0948\u0964 <\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"680\" src=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0004-1024x680.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-12056 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0004-1024x680.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0004-500x332.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0004-768x510.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0004-360x240.jpg 360w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0004.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<p><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#cd3636\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Do not Show Option<\/mark> \u0915\u0947 \u092e\u0926\u0926 \u0938\u0947 \u0906\u092a \u0905\u092a\u0928\u0947 Staff \u0915\u094b \u0909\u0928 \u091b\u0940\u091c\u094b \u0915\u093e Access \u0926\u0947 \u0938\u0915\u0924\u0947 \u0939\u0948 \u091c\u093f\u0928 \u092a\u0930 \u0915\u093e\u092e \u0915\u0930\u0924\u0947 \u0939\u0948\u0964 <br><br><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#cd3636\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Example<\/mark> \u0915\u0947 \u0932\u093f\u090f Store Manager \u0915\u094b \u0906\u092a Product \u0914\u0930 category \u0926\u0947 \u0938\u0915\u0924\u0947 \u0939\u0948\u0964 Delivery Boy \u0915\u094b Order Panel \u0926\u0947 \u0938\u0915\u0924\u0947 \u0939\u0948\u0964 \u0908\u0938\u0940 \u0924\u0930\u093e\u0939 \u0938\u0947 \u0906\u092a Billing Staff \u0915\u094b POS \u0926\u0947 \u0938\u0915\u0924\u0947 \u0939\u0948\u0964  <\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"919\" src=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0006-1024x919.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-12057 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ww